Sorry to miss touching base today.  Tomorrow morning would be better.  I
know you were looking for a few sentences about EB. Josh and I just wrote
this for a DOE survey:

The Ella Baker School (02M225) is preparing for the 2020-2021 school year
by utilizing both a blended model and a fully remote model for
instruction.  Due to the Covid-19 Pandemic all New York City Schools will
be using these models of instruction.

The Ella Baker School is a small pre-k to grade 8 school, dedicated
building on students' strengths through anti-racist, progressive curricula
and instruction.  Our foundations in progressive education and our trust in
children ensure that we use models that promote active engagement and
critical thinking.  Our ultimate goal is for Ella Baker graduates to
participate fully in our diverse democratic society and improve our world
for generations to come.

We use a variety of programs that align with our beliefs about children and
about learning.  Our instruction empowers students to seek multiple
perspectives, weigh and use evidence, question information, look for
patterns, ponder conjecture, determine relevance, and learn about
themselves and others.


And here is our mission statement:

   -
   -

    Ella Baker School's Mission
   At the Ella Baker School, our teachers, students and families
   collaborate to create a dynamic and joyful learning community. We provid=
e a
   strong intellectual foundation across multiple disciplines. Students
   construct meaning and deep understanding through inquiry, self discovery
   and experiential learning. Our practices promote critical and creative
   thinking, artistic expression, and a courageous commitment to diversity =
and
   social justice. We provide experiences and opportunities for students to
   find out who they are for themselves and within their world.
   -

Continuing the legacy of the progressive education movement, the Ella Baker
School prepares students to be informed, courageous, and compassionate
people, who trust and respect one another and in turn, help to shape a more
equitable and sustainable world.




Do these help?  As far as specific projects for any funding from David &
